These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, polish, russian, french
4 different pets are kept: fish, goat, snake, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the japanese##1
3. the polish is on the left or right of the russian##3
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the french is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
6. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
7. the polish is somewhere between the japanese and the owner of the goat##7
8. the polish and the owner of the goldfish have the same parity positions##9
9. the russian and the owner of the fish have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | japanese | polish | russian     | french |
| Pet           | snake   | goldfish     | goat | fish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, soy-milk, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting, reading, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is cooking and the person drinking fanta have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice     | soy-milk    | sprite | fanta    |
| Hobby      | woodworking | collecting | reading      | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, iced-tea, sprite
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, watermelon, blueberry, papaya
1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
2. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
8. the person drinking juice and the person eating watermelon have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | juice    | iced-tea   | lemonade    | sprite  |
| Food       | watermelon | papaya | grapefruit | blueberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, writer, project-manager, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, salsa, disco, dubstep
1. the fan rock is the writer##1
2. the fan salsa is on the right of the fan disco##1
3. the fan salsa is somewhere to the left of the writer##5
4. the fan dubstep is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
5. the fan salsa is on the left of the mechanic##1
6. the firefighter and the fan dubstep have the same parity positions##9
7. the project-manager is on the left or right of the mechanic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | firefighter | project-manager | mechanic  | writer |
| Music-Genre   | disco             | salsa          | dubstep | rock    |

