.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, jazz, funk, folk
4 different pets are kept: goat, snake, hamster, horse
1. the fan funk is not the owner of the hamster##6
2. the owner of the goat and the fan metal have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the snake and the fan jazz have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the fan funk##5
5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the fan folk##1
6. the fan jazz is not the owner of the snake##6
7. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan metal##1
9. the owner of the horse is not the fan folk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal | funk | folk  | jazz |
| Pet           | snake   | goat     | hamster | horse      |

