2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
4. the dutch and the person watching zombie movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching western movies and the dutch have different parity positions##9
6. the russian is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
7. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
8. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the canadian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | adventure | zombie | western |
| Nationality   | canadian        | russian    | dutch   | australian |

