The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, cycling, climbing, surfing
1. the fan rock is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##5
2. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is climbing##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing and the fan d&b have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the fan d&b is not to the right of the fan r&b##8
6. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5
7. the fan d&b is somewhere to the right of the fan soul##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | rock | d&b         | r&b     |
| Sport         | cycling | surfing  | climbing | rowing |

