.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, drawing, video-games
4 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, guinea-pig, turtle
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the lizard##7
2. the owner of the lizard is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the owner of the bird##6
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
7. the person who's hobby is video-games and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | video-games | rock-climbing | cooking | drawing |
| Pet     | lizard     | guinea-pig     | turtle     | bird    |

