.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, cranberry, asparagus, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, ship, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
2. the person eating zucchini and the person driving the airplane have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person eating cranberry is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the airplane##7
6. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | asparagus | eggplant   | cranberry | zucchini |
| Transport   | taxi   | ship | skateboard    | airplane      |

