.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, pineapple, carrot, plum
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, japanese, indonesian, polish
1. the person eating plum is not the polish##6
2. the polish is not to the right of the chinese##8
3. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person eating plum##8
4. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
6. the polish is on the far left##1
7. the chinese is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
8. the person eating cucumber is the japanese##1
9. the person eating plum and the chinese have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pineapple   | plum    | carrot | cucumber    |
| Nationality   | polish | chinese | indonesian   | japanese |

