The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, sports, satire, animation
1. the person watching zombie movies is not the person drinking mirinda##6
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
8. the person watching zombie movies and the person drinking milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching satire movies and the person drinking juice have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | water  | juice  | milk |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | satire | animation | zombie      |

