.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, sprite, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, country, electronic, disco
 1. the person drinking water and the fan electronic have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 3. the fan pop is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking fanta##7
 4. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan electronic is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea and the fan country have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan disco##3
 9. the fan disco is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan pop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta  | iced-tea | sprite  | water |
| Music-Genre   | disco | electronic     | pop | country     |

