2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is collecting have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
