.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, 7up, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, chess, collecting, rock-climbing
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 6. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the person drinking mirinda and the person who's hobby is chess have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 9. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is chess have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | 7up        | mirinda   | fanta      |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | collecting | chess | gardening |

 